    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We present a literature review and meta-analysis of relevant epidemiological parameters (24 for adults, 7 for children) of COVID-19. Standardization of these parameters is key to performing valid clinical and mathematical modeling, as well as forecasts, helping us to improve our understanding about the characteristics and impact of the pandemic.</jats:p>",
